cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "RateXp: Drop-in feedback collection for agentic skills"
message: "If you use RateXp, please cite it using the metadata below."
type: software
authors:
  - given-names: Hikmet
    family-names: Beyoglu
    email: hikmet.beyoglu@hotmail.com
repository-code: "https://github.com/HikmetB1/RateXp"
url: "https://github.com/HikmetB1/RateXp"
abstract: >-
  RateXp is a feedback collection solution for agentic skills. A skill author
  ships their skill with RateXp - pairing SKILL.md with an MCP client pointing to our core and a
  short feedback step - and it asks users for a rating and, with consent, the
  full conversation, redacts personal information, and shows the results on a
  live dashboard.
keywords:
  - agentic skills
  - feedback
  - dashboard
  - LLM
  - evaluation
